headline: Mondelez International at CAGNY: Cocoa Shock Spurs Reset, Reaffirms Long-Term Growth Targets
summary: Mondelez International (NASDAQ:MDLZ) used its presentation at the CAGNY conference to outline what executives described as a strengthened foundation for delivering the company’s long-term growth targets, while addressing recent performance pressures tied largely to unprecedented cocoa cost inflation
